channel.title: Quick help! anybody with 508 ip change client!
channel.description:
~MortalPK
Hello. Recently, I have made a private server, and do not know if it has been created correctly. I have done everything, and now i just need somebody to test if it works. If you have a 508 Ip changer Client, type in: [code]mortalpk.no-ip.biz[/code] I will be on the server, and if you can get on the server, [size=14pt][u][b]PLEASE, POST HERE[/b][/u][/size]. Tell me if you can or cannot connect. I really appreciate if somebody could help me. Thank you.
